    <step order="3" name="Plan the Upgrade">
      Document the upgrade plan in task notes (`notes/task-022-upgrade-plan.md`):
      - Removed code (R4 shim): `previewContainer` / `previewText` / `emptyState`
        styles, `MAX_INLINE_PREVIEW_CHARS` + truncation logic, the
        `&lt;Card&gt;`/`&lt;CardHeader&gt;`/`&lt;pre&gt;` JSX subtree that owns
